8-01-07T17:55:26.000Z","msg":"有時打機 同d街外人嘈完交 個人真係好舒暢好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f402883aec49ba5eeb71f1808312ec2cae63ace7","tid":522572,"uid":139139,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T17:56:03.000Z","msg":"香港人鍾意睇人仆街嘅原因<br />\n香港人鍾意笑鳩人嘅原因<br />\n香港人鍾意眼紅人哋嘅原因<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係因為我哋嘅教育制度<br />\n由細細個開始已經係比賽<br />\n永遠都想追求第一<br />\n所以打機，香港人永遠都想做出眾嘅一群。"},{"pid":"795b7ba0eb24dfca628d0b49339f99e4e27726fa","tid":522572,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9cb3f7b670f90fbe1302dd3cf94338991947537","tid":522572,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ab09c8285b9f738f9ac6df14a689c287f375998","tid":522572,"uid":105552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aada40dd043d0492f4af0ad59faef284b694c24a","tid":522572,"uid":11148,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T17:34:55.000Z","msg":"起左樓主底,發覺佢捱到今時今日仲生存緊好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T17:42:19.000Z","msg":"無計<br />\nthe game must go on<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T17:53:02.000Z","msg":"iktf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T17:59:07.000Z","msg":"雖然係廢話，但真係睇開d啦，做好自己，有餘力自再立人。將自己既道德觀加係其他人身上會變道德撚。"},{"pid":"c11563ba48f5acacc537e1b7bff9b984a7677611","tid":522572,"uid":142144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:17:03.000Z","msg":"好撚多仆街開外掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db1d117c4a3311e6b393600804e4f5652e232a2","tid":522572,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T18:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquot